author: iocanel
msg: [KARAF-1034] Fixed destroy methods so that cellar can cleanly uninstall. Added some lifecycle and npe checks.

author: minfrin
msg: mod_proxy: Make ap_proxy_retry_worker() into an optional function. Allows
and mod_lbmethod_heartbeat to be loaded without mod_proxy yet being present,
which happens when modules are loaded in alphabetical order.

author: iocanel
msg: [KARAF-1079] Fixed Hazlecast configuration manager to properly create sets from configuration properties. Added a unit tests that checks the isUpdated method of the configuratio manager. Added missing license headers.

author: hbetts
msg: Updated to reflect a patch attributed to LIBCLOUD-121 brining full compute support, PEP 8 compliance, and additional driver tests, for OpenNebula.org versions up to 3.2.
